      <odd id="aspace_f247803468c7596a7198720ce8f9279b">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Additions to this collection will consist of only materials printed or written in the French language, and pertaining to French life and culture. No items or portions of collections will be transferred from individial collections to this collection.</p>  
      </odd>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_98e65d4ff256ed9153a85154d0251f74">
